OL,3,CLiam Payne: The boy from Bushbury who
OL,4,Cbecame a global sensation
OL,6,FIt was a cold November night in 2009
OL,7,Fwhen I first met Liam Payne.
OL,9,FAt the time, I was working as the
OL,10,FEntertainment Correspondent for the
OL,11,FBlack Country's regional daily paper,
OL,12,Fthe Express & Star - and Liam was
OL,13,Fsimply a teenager who had an
OL,14,Funsuccessful run on X Factor the year
OL,15,Fbefore - suffering heartbreaking
OL,16,Frejection at the Judges House stage.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
