OL,3,CLiam Payne: The boy from Bushbury who
OL,4,Cbecame a global sensation
OL,6,FThe event was the Dudley town centre
OL,7,FChristmas lights switch-on, and Liam
OL,8,Fwas the opening act for the hotly-
OL,9,Fanticipated headliner - a remote-
OL,10,Fcontrolled animatronic called Titan
OL,11,Fthe Robot.
OL,13,FA rather inauspicious show compared to
OL,14,Fwhat would follow just a year later,
OL,15,Fbut at that moment in time, nobody had
OL,16,Fany idea what was to come.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
