OL,3,CLiam Payne: The boy from Bushbury who
OL,4,Cbecame a global sensation
OL,6,FI managed to grab a few words from
OL,7,Fhim. The news editors had insisted
OL,8,Fupon it - a boy from Bushbury,
OL,9,FWolverhampton, having been on X Factor
OL,10,Fand performing locally was sure to be
OL,11,Fof interest to our readers.
OL,13,FAnd despite his continuing
OL,14,Fdisappointment at missing out in 2008,
OL,15,Fand his dreams of stardom still
OL,16,Fburning bright, he was gracious,
OL,17,Ffriendly, and enthusiastic to speak to.
OL,19,F"It's a great crowd, I'm delighted to
OL,20,Fbe here," he told me.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
