OL,3,CLiam Payne: The boy from Bushbury who
OL,4,Cbecame a global sensation
OL,6,FOur interview was cut short when Titan
OL,7,Fmade his appearance. I can't lie - it
OL,8,Fwas something of a shock when, in
OL,9,FAutumn 2010, I realised that one of
OL,10,Fthat year's X Factor favourites was
OL,11,Fthe very same wide-eyed hopeful who
OL,12,Fhad been the support act for a robot
OL,13,Fjust months before.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
