OL,3,CLiam Payne: The boy from Bushbury who
OL,4,Cbecame a global sensation
OL,6,FAnd 2010 was a great year for the
OL,7,FMidlands on the show - not only was
OL,8,FLiam representing Wolverhampton, Cher
OL,9,FLloyd - from Malvern in Worcestershire
OL,10,F- was also hotly tipped for success;
OL,11,Fand Dudley's very own Wagner was that
OL,12,Fyear's comedic thorn in Simon Cowell's
OL,13,Fside.
OL,15,FIt meant I was kept busy, trying to
OL,16,Ftrack down friends and family who
OL,17,Fwould speak to me as their respective
OL,18,Fstars continued to rise.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
