OL,3,CLiam Payne: The boy from Bushbury who
OL,4,Cbecame a global sensation
OL,6,FIt wasn't, of course.
OL,8,FAs one-fifth of Cowell-created boyband
OL,9,FOne Direction, he finished in third
OL,10,Fplace that year.
OL,12,FAnd perhaps that was a blessing in
OL,13,Fdisguise, as they avoided the so-
OL,14,Fcalled "curse" which saw winners'
OL,15,Fcareers sky-rocket, and then fizzle
OL,16,Fout just as quickly.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
