OL,3,CLiam Payne: The boy from Bushbury who
OL,4,Cbecame a global sensation
OL,6,FAfter debut single What Makes You
OL,7,FBeautiful hit the number one spot in
OL,8,Fthe UK charts in 2011, going multi-
OL,9,Fplatinum, the group became regular
OL,10,Ffixtures in the Top 10 and accrued
OL,11,Fmillions of adoring fans around the
OL,12,Fworld.
OL,14,FI always kept half an eye out for when
OL,15,Fhe hit the headlines, and was half-
OL,16,Famused, half-sad when it was noted how
OL,17,Fhis Wolverhampton twang had
OL,18,Fdisappeared.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
