OL,3,CLiam Payne: The boy from Bushbury who
OL,4,Cbecame a global sensation
OL,6,FBut despite global superstardom, and
OL,7,Fhis well-documented struggles with
OL,8,Falcohol - about which he had been very
OL,9,Fhonest - it was clear he had a strong
OL,10,Flove for his roots.
OL,12,FHis former headteacher at St Peter's
OL,13,FCollegiate School, Huw Bishop, told
OL,14,Fthe Express & Star that Liam regularly
OL,15,Finvited him to One Direction shows - a
OL,16,Fway, perhaps, of thanking him for
OL,17,Fsigning the permission forms allowing
OL,18,Fhim to attend those early auditions in
OL,19,F2008.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
