OL,3,CLiam Payne: The boy from Bushbury who
OL,4,Cbecame a global sensation
OL,6,FI only met Liam once more - at the
OL,7,Fopening of HMV Birmingham in October
OL,8,F2019.
OL,10,FHe had seen reasonable success as a
OL,11,Fsolo artist, though nothing which
OL,12,Freached the heights of One Direction
OL,13,Ffever, and he spoke thoughtfully about
OL,14,Fthe impact which streaming had had on
OL,15,Fthe music industry.
OL,17,FHe went on to describe his hopes and
OL,18,Fplans for the future, as he tried to
OL,19,Fblaze his own trail, and I wished him
OL,20,Fwell.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
