OL,3,CLiam Payne: The boy from Bushbury who
OL,4,Cbecame a global sensation
OL,6,FI was incredibly sad to hear news of
OL,7,Fhis death. I can't claim to have known
OL,8,Fhim well, of course, but working in
OL,9,Fnews and entertainment often means you
OL,10,Fcross paths with extraordinarily
OL,11,Ftalented people - some of whom do go
OL,12,Fon to take the world by storm.
OL,14,FLiam was one of those people.
OL,16,FHe was a global pop sensation, part of
OL,17,Fa musical phenomenon - achieving the
OL,18,Fkind of success many can only ever
OL,19,Fdream of.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
